            "text": "Integrating Chatterbox into Microservices Ecosystems"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "When embedding Chatterbox in a microservices architecture, employ API gateways for centralized routing and observability. Use service meshes like Istio to manage traffic policies and implement retries with exponential backoff for fault tolerance. Ensure idempotency in API calls to handle duplicate requests safely."
          }
        ]
      },
