      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Track Chatterbox performance using metrics such as p99 latency, error rates, and CPU/memory utilization via tools like Prometheus. Scale horizontally by adding pods in Kubernetes based on custom metrics, and tune thread pools and connection timeouts to match workload patterns. Regularly audit API logs to identify bottlenecks and adjust caching strategies accordingly."
